<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" itunes:timing="Word"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><ttm:agent type="other" xml:id="v2"/><iTunesMetadata xmlns="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal"><songwriters><songwriter>Lin-Manuel Miranda</songwriter></songwriters></iTunesMetadata><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Who Lives, Who Dies, Who Tells Your Story"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Original Broadway Cast of Hamilton"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Hamilton (Original Broadway Cast Recording)"/><amll:meta key="appleMusicId" value="1025212508"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="35804644"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="7EsSVPxaYoAZjQwhspJBs2"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="004QCSMf3Vyc1f"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="42143735"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="MeTerminator"/></metadata></head><body dur="3:33.272"><div begin="4.655" end="3:33.272"><p begin="4.655" end="7.194" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="4.655" end="4.979">Let</span> <span begin="4.979" end="5.183">me</span> <span begin="5.183" end="5.541">tell</span> <span begin="5.541" end="5.720">you</span> <span begin="5.720" end="5.887">what</span> <span begin="5.887" end="6.078">I</span> <span begin="6.078" end="6.374">wish</span> <span begin="6.374" end="6.713">I&apos;d</span> <span begin="6.713" end="7.194">known</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">让我告诉你，我多么希望当初能明白一件事</span></p><p begin="7.861" end="10.926" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="7.861" end="8.123">When</span> <span begin="8.123" end="8.332">I</span> <span begin="8.332" end="8.539">was</span> <span begin="8.539" end="8.819">young</span> <span begin="8.819" end="9.057">and</span> <span begin="9.057" end="9.573">dreamed</span> <span begin="9.573" end="9.699">of</span> <span begin="9.699" end="10.926">glory</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">当我年轻并梦想着荣耀时</span></p><p begin="11.365" end="13.004" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="11.365" end="11.597">You</span> <span begin="11.597" end="11.853">have</span> <span begin="11.853" end="12.202">no</span> <span begin="12.202" end="13.004">control</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你无法掌控</span></p><p begin="13.014" end="17.685" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="13.014" end="13.414">Who</span> <span begin="13.414" end="13.910">lives,</span> <span begin="13.910" end="14.214">who</span> <span begin="14.214" end="14.729">dies,</span> <span begin="14.729" end="15.065">who</span> <span begin="15.065" end="15.577">tells</span> <span begin="15.577" end="15.947">your</span> <span begin="15.947" end="17.685">story?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">谁能活着，谁会死去，谁来讲述你的故事？</span></p><p begin="16.745" end="18.012" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="16.745" end="17.302">President</span> <span begin="17.302" end="18.012">Jefferson</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">杰斐逊总统：</span></p><p begin="18.154" end="21.759" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="18.154" end="18.404">I&apos;ll</span> <span begin="18.404" end="18.570">give</span> <span begin="18.570" end="18.773">him</span> <span begin="18.773" end="19.368">this,</span> <span begin="19.368" end="19.659">his</span> <span begin="19.659" end="20.207">financial</span> <span begin="20.207" end="20.593">system</span> <span begin="20.593" end="20.706">is</span> <span begin="20.706" end="20.837">a</span> <span begin="20.837" end="21.045">work</span> <span begin="21.045" end="21.208">of</span> <span begin="21.208" end="21.759">genius</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">“我得承认这一点，他的金融体系是一部天才之作”</span></p><p begin="21.788" end="23.607" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="21.788" end="22.020">I</span> <span begin="22.020" end="22.283">couldn&apos;t</span> <span begin="22.283" end="22.685">undo</span> <span begin="22.685" end="22.785">it</span> <span begin="22.785" end="23.002">if</span> <span begin="23.002" end="23.125">I</span> <span begin="23.125" end="23.607">tried</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">“就算我想废除也无能为力”</span></p><p begin="24.494" end="25.677" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="24.494" end="24.854">And</span> <span begin="24.977" end="25.193">I&apos;ve</span> <span begin="25.193" end="25.677">tried</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">“而且我确实尝试过”</span></p><p begin="26.176" end="30.847" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="26.176" end="26.576">Who</span> <span begin="26.576" end="27.072">lives,</span> <span begin="27.072" end="27.376">who</span> <span begin="27.376" end="27.891">dies,</span> <span begin="27.891" end="28.227">who</span> <span begin="28.227" end="28.739">tells</span> <span begin="28.739" end="29.109">your</span> <span begin="29.109" end="30.847">story?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">谁能活着，谁会死去，谁来讲述你的故事？</span></p><p begin="29.857" end="30.997" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="29.857" end="30.406">President</span> <span begin="30.406" end="30.997">Madison</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">麦迪逊总统：</span></p><p begin="31.028" end="33.919" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="31.028" end="31.337">He</span> <span begin="31.337" end="31.522">took</span> <span begin="31.522" end="31.742">our</span> <span begin="31.742" end="32.125">country</span> <span begin="32.125" end="32.277">from</span> <span begin="32.277" end="32.979">bankruptcy</span> <span begin="32.979" end="33.134">to</span> <span begin="33.134" end="33.919">prosperity</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">“他让我们的国家从破产走向繁荣”</span></p><p begin="34.347" end="35.277" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="34.347" end="34.526">I</span> <span begin="34.526" end="34.734">hate</span> <span begin="34.734" end="34.881">to</span> <span begin="34.881" end="35.132">admit</span> <span begin="35.132" end="35.277">it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">“虽然我讨厌承认”</span></p><p begin="35.687" end="38.818" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="35.687" end="35.901">But</span> <span begin="35.901" end="36.125">he</span> <span begin="36.125" end="36.395">doesn&apos;t</span> <span begin="36.395" end="36.560">get</span> <span begin="36.560" end="36.859">enough</span> <span begin="36.859" end="37.121">credit</span> <span begin="37.121" end="37.371">for</span> <span begin="37.371" end="37.609">all</span> <span begin="37.609" end="37.781">the</span> <span begin="37.781" end="38.114">credit</span> <span begin="38.114" end="38.329">he</span> <span begin="38.329" end="38.596">gave</span> <span begin="38.596" end="38.818">us</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">“但他为我们建立的那些信用（贷款），并没有让他得到应有的赞誉”</span></p><p begin="39.300" end="43.928" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="39.300" end="39.657">Who</span> <span begin="39.657" end="40.153">lives,</span> <span begin="40.153" end="40.457">who</span> <span begin="40.457" end="40.972">dies,</span> <span begin="40.972" end="41.308">who</span> <span begin="41.308" end="41.820">tells</span> <span begin="41.820" end="42.190">your</span> <span begin="42.190" end="43.928">story?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">谁能活着，谁会死去，谁来讲述你的故事？</span></p><p begin="42.991" end="45.753" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="42.991" end="43.452">Every</span> <span begin="43.452" end="43.723">other</span> <span begin="43.723" end="44.215">founding</span> <span begin="44.215" end="44.587">father</span> <span begin="44.587" end="45.050">story</span> <span begin="45.050" end="45.266">gets</span> <span begin="45.266" end="45.753">told</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">其他每一位国父的故事都被传颂</span></p><p begin="46.164" end="48.936" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="46.164" end="46.591">Every</span> <span begin="46.591" end="47.007">other</span> <span begin="47.007" end="47.407">founding</span> <span begin="47.407" end="47.823">father</span> <span begin="47.823" end="48.138">gets</span> <span begin="48.138" end="48.306">to</span> <span begin="48.306" end="48.556">grow</span> <span begin="48.556" end="48.936">old</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">其他每一位国父都得以安享晚年</span></p><p begin="49.611" end="51.956" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="49.611" end="49.807">And</span> <span begin="49.807" end="49.980">when</span> <span begin="49.980" end="50.176">you&apos;re</span> <span begin="50.176" end="50.563">gone,</span> <span begin="50.563" end="50.783">who</span> <span begin="50.783" end="51.402">remembers</span> <span begin="51.402" end="51.586">your</span> <span begin="51.586" end="51.956">name?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">当你离去，谁会记住你的名字？</span></p><p begin="52.043" end="57.175" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="52.043" end="52.443">Who</span> <span begin="52.443" end="52.909">keeps</span> <span begin="52.909" end="53.259">your</span> <span begin="53.259" end="53.709">flame?</span> <span begin="53.709" end="54.071">Who</span> <span begin="54.071" end="54.503">tells</span> <span begin="54.503" end="54.827">your</span> <span begin="54.827" end="56.501">story?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">谁来守护你的火种？谁来讲述你的故事？</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="55.226" end="57.175"><span begin="55.226" end="55.594">(Who</span> <span begin="55.594" end="56.048">tells</span> <span begin="56.048" end="56.394">your</span> <span begin="56.394" end="57.175">story?)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">谁来讲述你的故事？</span></span></p><p begin="56.775" end="1:00.909" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="56.775" end="57.178">Who</span> <span begin="57.178" end="57.652">tells</span> <span begin="57.652" end="58.013">your</span> <span begin="58.013" end="59.027">sto</span><span begin="59.027" end="1:00.909">ry?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">谁来讲述你的故事？</span></p><p begin="1:01.830" end="1:07.333" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="1:03.815" end="1:04.075">I</span> <span begin="1:04.075" end="1:04.341">put</span> <span begin="1:04.341" end="1:04.932">myself</span> <span begin="1:04.932" end="1:05.157">back</span> <span begin="1:05.157" end="1:05.392">in</span> <span begin="1:05.392" end="1:05.675">the</span> <span begin="1:05.675" end="1:06.040">narra</span><span begin="1:06.040" end="1:07.333">tive</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我将自己重新放入这段叙事之中</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="1:01.830" end="1:04.015"><span begin="1:01.830" end="1:04.015">(Eliza)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">伊莉莎</span></span></p><p begin="1:08.368" end="1:11.896" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="1:09.365" end="1:09.579">I</span> <span begin="1:09.579" end="1:10.008">stop</span> <span begin="1:10.008" end="1:10.483">wasting</span> <span begin="1:10.483" end="1:10.926">time</span> <span begin="1:10.926" end="1:11.168">on</span> <span begin="1:11.168" end="1:11.896">tears</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我不再把时间浪费在眼泪上</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="1:08.368" end="1:10.765"><span begin="1:08.368" end="1:10.765">(Eliza)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">伊莉莎</span></span></p><p begin="1:11.896" end="1:16.961" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="1:11.896" end="1:12.108">I</span> <span begin="1:12.108" end="1:12.366">live</span> <span begin="1:12.366" end="1:12.756">another</span> <span begin="1:12.756" end="1:13.513">fifty</span> <span begin="1:13.513" end="1:14.322">years,</span> <span begin="1:14.322" end="1:14.540">it&apos;s</span> <span begin="1:14.540" end="1:14.781">not</span> <span begin="1:14.781" end="1:15.516">enough</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我又活了五十年，但这还不够</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="1:14.895" end="1:16.961"><span begin="1:14.895" end="1:16.961">(Eliza)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">伊莉莎</span></span></p><p begin="1:15.861" end="1:20.375" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="1:15.861" end="1:16.190">I</span> <span begin="1:16.190" end="1:16.956">interview</span> <span begin="1:16.956" end="1:17.592">every</span> <span begin="1:17.592" end="1:18.226">soldier</span> <span begin="1:18.226" end="1:18.467">who</span> <span begin="1:18.467" end="1:18.865">fought</span> <span begin="1:18.865" end="1:19.086">by</span> <span begin="1:19.086" end="1:19.264">your</span> <span begin="1:19.264" end="1:20.375">side</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我采访了每一位曾并肩与你作战的士兵</span></p><p begin="1:19.523" end="1:22.812" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="1:19.523" end="1:20.018">She</span> <span begin="1:20.018" end="1:20.367">tells</span> <span begin="1:20.367" end="1:20.802">our</span> <span begin="1:20.802" end="1:22.812">story</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">她讲述着我们的故事</span></p><p begin="1:21.338" end="1:25.246" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="1:21.338" end="1:21.576">I</span> <span begin="1:21.576" end="1:22.074">try</span> <span begin="1:22.074" end="1:22.174">to</span> <span begin="1:22.174" end="1:22.367">make</span> <span begin="1:22.367" end="1:22.790">sense</span> <span begin="1:22.790" end="1:22.891">of</span> <span begin="1:22.891" end="1:23.123">your</span> <span begin="1:23.123" end="1:23.748">thousands</span> <span begin="1:23.748" end="1:24.003">of</span> <span begin="1:24.003" end="1:24.521">pages</span> <span begin="1:24.521" end="1:24.812">of</span> <span begin="1:24.812" end="1:25.246">writings</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我试图理清你留下的那几千页手稿</span></p><p begin="1:25.336" end="1:28.568" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="1:25.336" end="1:25.647">You</span> <span begin="1:25.647" end="1:26.074">really</span> <span begin="1:26.074" end="1:26.375"